<span class="postbody">Keep in mind that the advantage of the new pet haste spell is not so much the haste/buffage it provides but the duration.
<br />

<br />

<br />

<br />
Sha's Ferocity is 17.5 minutes duration and 350 mana where as Arag's Celerity is 45 minutes (almost 3 times as long) for just 100 mana more.  
<br />

<br />

<br />

<br />
So instead you end up using 450 mana in 45 minutes compared to ~1050 mana over the same amount of time using Sha's Ferocity.  That along with minor but not bad increases in STR, AC, and ATK.
<br />

<br />

<br />

<br />
The longer recast time also makes it easier to give up that spell slot for a more practical spell.   
<br />

<br />
Circle of the Ancient
